nk as part of the epidemiological study in the surrounding area of the infected farm.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://promedmail.org/promed-post/?id=8015608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpromedmail.org%2Fpromed-post%2F%3Fid%3D8015608&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzDDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=9b40ea3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://promedmail.org/promed-post/?id=8015608</a>"},{"pid":"47166cae0cc5c1177acb820b0d1593851555975a","tid":2334874,"uid":134687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"仲唔打9 ccp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325fc0bc0742eb08b410a5edb71a866ca3227494","tid":2334874,"uid":189374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:34:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/StockMKTNewz/status/1341013526811439105?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStockMKTNewz%2Fstatus%2F1341013526811439105%3Fs%3D20&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzDDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=ec6240af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStockMKTNewz%2Fstatus%2F1341013526811439105%3Fs%3D20&h=f250b167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/StockMKTNewz/status/1341013526811439105?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />超過一半&quot;借&quot;番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a834b7ee162b89aa1dcd2cc5bf17794dddf32e","tid":2334874,"uid":266918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcca12b2c31c1de5b4d72cb0a6471c70beef5f01","tid":2334874,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"根據美國農業部（USDA）發布的警報，首例已知非圈養野生動物感染COVID-19的病例如今已經確診。該警報表示，在篩檢猶他州爆發疫情的皮草養殖場周圍的野生動物時，<span class=\"red\">有一隻野生水貂被檢測出陽性。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國農業部國家獸醫檢驗中心（National Veterinary Services Laboratory）負責進行檢測，根據該中心的說法，那隻野生水貂與猶他州周遭養殖場內感染水貂體內的病毒株是「無法區別」的。<br />\n<br />\n在美國，猶他州、威斯康辛州、奧瑞岡州、密西根州的16間水貂養殖場都有冠狀病毒疫情的紀錄，其中以猶他州的病例最多。不過，儘管在有疫情的養殖場周遭的水貂、浣熊、臭鼬及其他動物持續受到檢測，但直到現在才檢測出野生水貂的病例。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">這種病毒也出現在許多圈養的野生動物身上，包括獅子、老虎、雪豹，以及家養的犬貓。</span>科學家正在加緊速度確認還有哪些動物可能容易感染病毒，他們特別關注瀕危物種以及可能將病毒傳回給人類的物種。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"入左食物鏈，人類係咪要滅絕啦？"},{"pid":"95e8705c0de7bcf6494c0ce96565447133f48336","tid":2334874,"uid":314184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:35:10.000Z","msg":"武肺病毒跟本就係生化武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa0927d1be7c7849bf6006f943a9c168b1af46d","tid":2334874,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"325fc0bc0742eb08b410a5edb71a866ca3227494","tid":2334874,"uid":189374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:34:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/StockMKTNewz/status/1341013526811439105?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStockMKTNewz%2Fstatus%2F1341013526811439105%3Fs%3D20&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzDDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=ec6240af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStockMKTNewz%2Fstatus%2F1341013526811439105%3Fs%3D20&h=f250b167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/StockMKTNewz/status/1341013526811439105?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />超過一半&quot;借&quot;番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:36:13.000Z","msg":"無睇幾年，$21000咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c058efed23abe36b56a465bb51c1780fffa9380b","tid":2334874,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa22fd06c15cc28787e2290d884183410538e3b","tid":2334874,"uid":67896,"like":111,"dislike":15,"score":96,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:13:17.000Z","msg":"好人好者唔去食啲野生動物邊會出事<br />\n全世界得啲弱智國家先會咬開隻蝙蝠